            "title": "大埔宏福苑五級火｜中原慈善基金撥款300萬為受災學童提供緊急援助",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"大埔宏福苑五級火｜中原慈善基金撥款300萬為受災學童提供緊急援助\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/YEOxI_fUeTIEsEWhRCDUpA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/am730_578/1a06431d8022828da761e0df0bfda07e\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">大埔宏福苑五級火｜中原慈善基金撥款300萬為受災學童提供緊急援助</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">大埔宏福苑發生五級火災，造成多人傷亡，多個家庭受影響。中原集團向受災居民及其家屬致以最深切的慰問，會為協助受災家庭，「中原慈善基金」決定撥款300萬元，為每位受災學童提供3,000元的緊急援助，幫助他們的學習和生活需要。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 AM730 <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.am730.com.hk/地產/大埔宏福苑五級火-中原慈善基金撥款300萬為受災學童提供緊急援助/623246?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/地產/大埔宏福苑五級火-中原慈善基金撥款300萬為受災學童提供緊急援助/623246?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/地產/大埔宏福苑五級火-中原慈善基金撥款300萬為受災學童提供緊急援助/623246?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E5%AE%8F%E7%A6%8F%E8%8B%91%E4%BA%94%E7%B4%9A%E7%81%AB-%E4%B8%AD%E5%8E%9F%E6%85%88%E5%96%84%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE300%E8%90%AC%E7%82%BA%E5%8F%97%E7%81%BD%E5%AD%B8%E7%AB%A5%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E6%8F%B4%E5%8A%A9-122503771.html",
